---
// Features Section - Bento Grid
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div data-animate class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end gap-6 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <div>
        <span class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500 font-semibold mb-3 sm:mb-4 block">
          Por qué elegirnos
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-display">
          Ecosistema de Éxito para
          <span class="text-neutral-500 block mt-1">Modelos Webcam en Soacha</span>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-neutral-400 max-w-md md:text-right">
        No solo te damos una habitación. Te damos las herramientas, tecnología y soporte para construir tu carrera como modelo webcam profesional.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bento Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-5">
      
      <!-- Main Feature Card (Large) with Glass Effect -->
      <div 
        data-animate
        class="lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2 spotlight-card rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl border border-white/10 p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between bg-gradient-to-br from-white/[0.06] to-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-xl hover:border-amber-500/30 transition-all duration-500 relative overflow-hidden group min-h-[300px] sm:min-h-[400px]"
        style="box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05), inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.02);"
      >
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-500 mb-4 sm:mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-500">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-7 sm:h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 sm:mb-4 font-display">Maximización de Ingresos</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-6 sm:mb-8 max-w-md">
            Nuestro equipo de monitores analiza tu tráfico en tiempo real. Ajustamos precios, etiquetas y horarios para que nunca pierdas oportunidades de alto valor.
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 text-xs sm:text-sm text-white">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span>Estrategias SEO internas para mejor posicionamiento</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 text-xs sm:text-sm text-white">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span>Gestión multiplataforma simultánea</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 text-xs sm:text-sm text-white">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 text-amber-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span>Análisis de audiencia y optimización</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Decorative Chart -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[200px] sm:w-[300px] h-[150px] sm:h-[200px] opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" class="w-full h-full stroke-amber-500 fill-none stroke-2">
            <path d="M0,100 C30,90 50,85 80,60 S120,30 150,25 S180,20 200,10"></path>
            <path d="M0,100 C40,95 60,90 100,70 S140,50 170,45 S190,40 200,35" class="opacity-50"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Small Feature Cards with Glass Effect -->
      <div 
        data-animate
        class="spotlight-card rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-5 sm:p-6 flex flex-col justify-between bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-xl hover:border-indigo-500/30 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all duration-500 group min-h-[180px]"
        style="box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.2), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04);"
      >
        <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2 font-display">Geobloqueo Total</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
            Nadie en Colombia puede ver tu transmisión. Privacidad garantizada por IP.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div 
        data-animate
        class="spotlight-card rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-5 sm:p-6 flex flex-col justify-between bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-xl hover:border-pink-500/30 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all duration-500 group min-h-[180px]"
        style="box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.2), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04);"
      >
        <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl bg-pink-500/10 border border-pink-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-pink-400 mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2 font-display">Fotos Profesionales</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
            Sesiones mensuales para renovar tu perfil y atraer más tráfico.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wide Card with Glass Effect -->
      <div 
        data-animate
        class="lg:col-span-2 spotlight-card rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-5 sm:p-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-xl hover:border-emerald-500/30 hover:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all duration-500 group relative overflow-hidden"
        style="box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.2), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04);"
      >
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 mb-2">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 10h18M7 15h1m4 0h1m-7 4h12a3 3 0 003-3V8a3 3 0 00-3-3H6a3 3 0 00-3 3v8a3 3 0 003 3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-white font-display">Pagos Flexibles y Puntuales</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-neutral-400 pl-0 sm:pl-14">
            Recibe tus ganancias en Bancolombia, Nequi o USDT (Cripto). Pagos quincenales sin excepciones.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute right-[-30px] bottom-[-30px] sm:right-[-20px] sm:bottom-[-20px] text-emerald-500/10">
          <svg class="w-24 h-24 sm:w-36 sm:h-36" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1.41 16.09V20h-2.67v-1.93c-1.71-.36-3.16-1.46-3.27-3.4h1.96c.1 1.05.82 1.87 2.65 1.87 1.96 0 2.4-.98 2.4-1.59 0-.83-.44-1.61-2.67-2.14-2.48-.6-4.18-1.62-4.18-3.67 0-1.72 1.39-2.84 3.11-3.21V4h2.67v1.95c1.86.45 2.79 1.86 2.85 3.39H14.3c-.05-1.11-.64-1.87-2.22-1.87-1.5 0-2.4.68-2.4 1.64 0 .84.65 1.39 2.67 1.91s4.18 1.39 4.18 3.91c-.01 1.83-1.38 2.83-3.12 3.16z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
